          "reviewTitle": "Reliable soft all day coverage",
          "reviewText": "My dermatologist's office stopped selling this brand, so I was very happy to be able to order it from Amazon. Use a kabuki brush, and the coverage is VERY good. As good as a concealer (I do not use this under my eyes). Even though I usually wear pink tones, it is the Golden Light that matches my fair, Winter skin the best. I've been using Glo compacts for many many years. Just don't drop it. The cake of powder does break up pretty easily if you drop it hard. On my skin, this powder does not look cakey, or settle into my wrinkles and creases. And it stays on all day.",
